 Lately, a video showing more than 1,000 workers completed the transformation of Huangtai Station on the Qingdao-Ji'nan railway line in just six hours went viral on the Chinese internet. An online feedback says it showed the power of China as a "great infrastructure builder". Video credit to "Zhang Kaihua's Weibo", posted on Chinese social media platform Weibo (the Chinese version of Twitter). (Source: Weibo) 